<section>
  <span class="attribution">Gamma, E. et al. (1994, p. 81ff)</span>
  <h1>Creational</h1>

  <p><i>Abstract the instantiation process</i></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Make the system independent of how components are created</li>
    <li>Class pattern: Uses inheritance to vary the class' instantiation</li>
    <li>Creational Pattern: Delegate instantiation</li>
    <li>Composition over Inheritance</li>
  </ul>
</section>

