<section>
  <span class="attribution">Gamma, E. et al. (1994, p. 221)</span>
  <h1>Behavioral</h1>

  <i>Concerned with algorithms and the assignment of responsibilities</i>
  <ul>
    <li>Patterns of communication between behaviors</li>
    <li>Characterize complex control flow that's difficult to follow at run-time</li>
    <li>Shift focus from flow of control to how things are connected</li>
  </ul>
</section>

