<section>
  <h1>Discussion</h1>

  <ul>
    <li class="fragment">Are you maybe already using a pattern without knowing?</li>
    <li class="fragment">Better able to spot scope of a technique?</li>
    <li class="fragment">Do you (dis)agree with <i>my</i> interpretation?</li>
    <li class="fragment">Are my examples hitting the intention of design
      patterns?</li>
    <li class="fragment">Design patterns as tools?</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section>
  <h1>Application</h1>

  <ul>
    <li class="fragment">Use them reactive - not proactive</li>
    <li class="fragment">Do not use technical language (<code>@strategy</code>)
      - use domain language</li>
    <li class="fragment">Do they solve the problem you are facing or not?</li>
    <li class="fragment">Use the right "tool" - don't abuse</li>
  </ul>
</section>

